# This package no longer uses a single shared .env.
#
# Each demo lives in examples/<name>/ and carries its own scoped .env.example.
# To run a demo, copy that folder's example file and fill in only the vars it needs:
#
#   cp examples/stream/.env.example examples/stream/.env
#   bun run demo:stream
#
# Scripts cd into the example folder, so Bun auto-loads examples/<name>/.env.
# See README.md for the full list of demos and the CLI login flow.
